I worked on this project in spurts, so it didn't progress continuously the entire three years.  Yet, I'm glad it's finally reached a finishing point where there are no further features I can think of to add without bloating the module unnecessarily.  <br><br>If anyone is trying to make a roguelike I would say RL-Dice combined with <a href="https://love2d.org/wiki/RotLove" class="postlink">https://love2d.org/wiki/RotLove</a> would be an excellent one-two combo!  <br><blockquote class="uncited"><div>Thanks for all your hard work, I found this really useful.</div></blockquote>Great!  I'm glad there are people finding it helpful!!!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=36863">Codex</a> — Fri Jul 01, 2016 12:42 am</p><hr />
